name: Vans Slip-On Checkerboard
description: The Classic Slip-On 'Checkerboard' features significant throwback inspiration. The look was created in 1970s after Steve Van Doren noticed that teenage skaters were coloring checkerboards on their shoes. The pattern emerges on the forefoot and heel, with off-white on the quarter panel and padded collar. A white vulcanized midsole gives way to a gum rubber outsole, with a red heel bumper providing a hit of color.

name: Vans Authentic Golden Coast
description: The Authentic 'Golden Coast' features a black and white checkerboard pattern throughout its canvas upper. Supported by metal eyelets, a white vulcanized midsole gives way to a waffle outsole underfoot.

name: Jordan 1 Retro High Off-White University Blue
description: Inspired by the alma mater of Michael Jordan, the Off-White x Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG 'UNC' holds a classic structure of two tones, filtered through the distinctive design prism of Virgil Abloh. The method includes taking a white leather foundation with blue overlays of dark powder and adding embellishments that express an expressive, handmade value. They include separated wings, a floating Swoosh, and text lines on the quarter panel on the medial side delineating the shoe's taxonomy.

name: Vans Old Skool Yacht Club
description: Bringing a boldly color-blocked aesthetic to a classic silhouette, the Old Skool ‘Yacht Club’ features canvas quarter panels in kelly green, a suede toe cap and heel (in blue and yellow, respectively), and a leather sidestripe in white. Inspired by nautical flags, the sneaker is finished off with a white rubber midsole and red ‘Off the Wall’ logo on the heel.

name: Vans Old Skool Triple Black
description: Vans' iconic Old Skool silhouette gets a monochromatic makeover with the Old Skool 'Black.' Featuring a canvas upper in black, a tonal leather jazz-stripe cuts through the quarter panel. Reinforced at the toe box and heel, the shoe is supported by a padded tongue and collar as well as a vulcanized midsole. The gum-colored waffle-traction outsole provides the only differentiating color.

name: Vans Classic Slip On Black
description: First seen in 1977 and inspired by boat shoes, the Vans Classic Slip-On was originally known as 'Style 98.' This version is built with a classic black canvas upper, a padded collar and Vans’ signature gum waffle outsole. The Vans Off-the-Wall bumper logo on the heel keeps the iconic look intact.

name: Nike Air Max 97 Off-White Menta
description: The OFF-WHITE x Air Max 97 ‘Menta’ collab features a translucent textile upper wrapped in Wolf Grey, complemented by Virgil Abloh’s signature text and tonal zigzag stitching throughout. The neutral color palette is punctuated by a multicolored Swoosh that transitions from green to blue to red, while a smoky grey rubber outsole maintains the shoe’s translucent theme underfoot.

name: Converse Chuck Taylor All Star 70 Ox Black White
make: Converse Chuck Taylor All Star 70 Ox
description: No description available.

name: Vans Authentic True White
description: Known as the Van Doren Rubber Company in 1966, the two brothers Paul Van Doren and Jim Van Doren created the legendary Vans brand. Not long after the company was born, the #44 Deck Shoe arrived, now called the Vans Authentic sneaker. The model showcases a woven canvas upper, tonal eyelets, a padded footbed, and vulcanized rubber outsole. This version is clean and simple with a simple white upper displaying a Vans logo for contrast.

name: Converse Chuck Taylor All Star Hi Optical White
make: Converse Chuck Taylor All Star Hi
description: The Converse All Star Hi Optic White is a classic sneaker that has been a staple in the fashion industry for decades. The shoe features a white canvas upper with the iconic Chuck Taylor patch on the ankle. The white rubber sole provides excellent traction and durability, making it perfect for everyday wear. The shoe is made with high-quality materials that ensure longevity and comfort. The canvas upper is breathable and lightweight, while the rubber sole provides excellent shock absorption and support. The shoe is available in a range of sizes, making it suitable for both men and women. The Converse All Star Hi Optic White was released on January 20, 2017, and retails for $60. The shoe is a timeless classic that never goes out of style, making it a great investment for any sneaker enthusiast. Something we love about Converse All Star Hi Optic White is its versatility. It can be dressed up or down, making it suitable for any occasion. Our experts think the best features of the shoe are its durability and comfort. The standout feature of the Converse All Star Hi Optic White is its iconic design, which has remained unchanged for decades. Our experts especially love the shoe's ability to transcend trends and remain a timeless classic.

name: Converse Chuck Taylor All Star 70 Ox Comme des Garcons PLAY Multi-Heart White
make: Converse Chuck Taylor All Star 70 Ox
model: Comme des Garcons PLAY Multi-Heart White
description: The Comme des Garçons Play x Chuck 70 Low Top 'Multi Heart' features an eye-catching design against an off-white canvas backdrop. The upper is plastered with multiple iterations of the CDG Play hearts-and-eyes logo in a traditional red finish, complemented by a black heel strip for an added dash of contrasting color. A vulcanized rubber midsole in matching off-white gives way to a gum rubber outsole.

name: Converse Chuck Taylor All Star 70 Hi Off-White
make: Converse Chuck Taylor All Star 70 Hi
description: Virgil Abloh emphasizes accessibility and wearability with the OFF-WHITE x Chuck 70 ‘White’ collab. As a result, the classic silhouette is ensconced in traditional cotton canvas and finished in a versatile crisp white shade. Virgil retains the shoe’s signature and rubber license plate, though the latter is turned upside down. Additional flourishes include the OFF-WHITE’s trademark diagonal midsole stripes, printed text on the medial side, and a bright orange outsole.

name: Converse Chuck Taylor All Star 70 Hi Comme des Garcons PLAY Multi-Heart Green
make: Converse Chuck Taylor All Star 70 Hi
model: Comme des Garcons PLAY Multi-Heart Green
description: A collaboration between Comme des Garçons and Converse, the Comme des Garçons Play x Chuck 70 Hi Top 'Multi Heart' features the signature heart logos rotated throughout base of the shoe. The canvas upper otherwise appears in khaki, with solid black on the fabric heel strip. Metal eyelets support the lacing system, with the toe cap leading into a vulcanized midsole. A diamond pattern on the outsole provides traction.

name: adidas Yeezy Boost 700 Wave Runner (Kids)
description: The Yeezy Boost 700 Kids 'Wave Runner,' originally revealed at the Season 5 runway show, emerges here in kids' sizes. The shoe maintains the look of its full-size counterparts, with a mesh upper in Solid Grey and teal overlaid by suede and leather in Solid Grey and black. The breathable build is accented by neon laces, while underfoot, the colorful midsole houses a Boost unit for cushioning. A herringbone pattern on the outsole provides traction.

name: Jordan 5 Retro Off-White Muslin
description: A collaboration between Virgil Abloh and Jordan Brand, the OFF-WHITE x Air Jordan 5 SP 'Muslin' is a stylized take on the silhouette. Built with faded black textile, the upper includes reflective silver detailing on the tongue. The laces and medial side sport Abloh's signature text, while underfoot, the outsole sports a pre-yellowed aesthetic.

name: Nike P-6000 Metallic Silver
description: The Nike P-6000 'Metallic Silver' brings a silver mesh upper with chrome-colored synthetic leather overlays. A floating Swoosh is piped in black. The full-length foam midsole works with a black rubber, herringbone-patterned outsole.

name: Vans Authentic Black Canvas
description: Known as the #44 Deck Shoe, the Vans Authentic sneakers debuted as part of the Van Doren Rubber Company — now known as Vans. This 1966 low-top design grew immensely popular in Southern California skate culture, These shoes are now reborn in a blackout version that keeps true to the original details, from the canvas upper and metal eyelets to the ‘Off The Wall’ heel bumper logo and the classic waffle outsole.

name: Converse Chuck Taylor All Star 70 Hi Black
make: Converse Chuck Taylor All Star 70 Hi
description: No description available.

description: No description available.

name: Nike Air Force 1 Low Supreme White
description: The Supreme x Air Force 1 Low 'Box Logo - White' released as part of the New York brand's Spring/Summer 2020 collection. The shoe's upper is built with leather, finished in white and highlighted by Supreme's signature box logo on the lateral heel. The custom sockliner and a second set of laces sport further Supreme branding, while Air in the heel of the midsole provides cushioning.

name: Nike Air Force 1 Low Supreme Black
description: Originally debuting as part of Supreme's Spring/Summer 2020 collection, the Supreme x Air Force 1 Low 'Box Logo - Black' released in March 2020. The shoe's full-grain leather upper appears in black, accented by Supreme's red box logo on the lateral heel. The custom sockliner and additional set of laces sport further Supreme branding, while the midsole houses the usual Air for cushioning.

name: Converse Run Star Hike Hi Black White Gum
description: No description available.

name: Jordan 1 Retro High OG University Blue
description: Paying tribute to Michael Jordan's college alma mater, the Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG 'University Blue' features a University of North Carolina look. Built entirely with leather, the shoe's upper appears in a mix of white and University Blue, contrasted by black on the Swoosh, collar, laces and 'Wings' logo. Perforations on the toe box provide breathability, while underfoot, the Air midsole gives way to a concentric outsole with a brighter shade of blue.

name: Jordan 4 Retro Off-White Sail (Women's)
description: The OFF-WHITE x Wmns Air Jordan 4 Retro SP 'Sail' released as part of a collaboration between Virgil Abloh's luxury brand and Jordan Brand. The classic basketball silhouette emerges with a deconstructed leather build, finished in off-white and complemented by semi-translucent TPU on the eyelets, wings and heel panel. A tonal zip-tie and 'Air' above the visible cushioning complete the look.

name: Jordan 1 Low Grey Toe (GS)
description: No description available.

name: Jordan 5 Retro Off-White Sail
description: Jordan Brand teamed up with Virgil Abloh's luxury streetwear label to create the Off-White x Air Jordan 5 Retro 'Fire Red' in October 2020. A follow-up to an early 2020 Air Jordan 5 collaboration, the shoe's upper features an off-white textile construction, with the midfoot, collar and reflective silver tongue sporting circular cutouts. Helvetica text marks the medial side, while underfoot, a contrasting black midsole houses Air in the heel for cushioning. A pre-yellowed finish on the outsole, which provides traction, completes the look.

name: Nike SB Dunk Low Pro J-Pack Chicago
description: The Nike Dunk Low SB 'J-Pack Chicago' takes design cues from the Air Jordan 1, using a white base with red overlays on the forefoot and heel. A contrasting black Swoosh and Nike-branded back tab add in the final Bulls-inspired colors. The foam midsole packs a Zoom Air unit in the heel for a lightweight feel, while a rubber cupsole pairs with white sidewalls and a red rubber outsole.

name: Jordan 11 Retro Jubilee (GS)
description: The Air Jordan 11 'Jubilee' for grade schoolers marks the twenty-fifth birthday of this iconic silhouette with an all-black design across the upper in the usual combination of ballistic mesh and patent leather. These mid-top sneakers rest on a traditional white foam midsole, bolstered by a translucent rubber outsole. To commemorate the shoe's silver anniversary, the word 'Jordan' is elegantly spelled out in silver on each of the shoe's eyelets, while a 3D metallic Jumpman logo and corresponding '23' branding embellish the heel.

name: Nike Dunk Low Retro White Black Panda (GS)
description: The Dunk Low GS 'Black White' brings a classic two-tone colorway to the basketball classic. A grade-school iteration of the shoe, the upper appears in a mix of black and white on its leather construction, with a lightly padded tongue for support. Underfoot, a white low-profile midsole gives way to a concentric black rubber outsole, which takes its traction pattern from the Air Jordan 1.

name: Nike Dunk Low Retro White Black Panda
description: The Dunk Low 'Black White' also known as 'Panda' brings a classic two-tone look to its classic basketball construction. The shoe's low-top build emerges in leather, with a white base contrasted by black overlays, with further black on the Swoosh branding. Perforations on the toe box provide breathability, while underfoot, the two-tone look is matched by the tooling, which incorporates a concentric rubber outsole for traction.

name: Nike Dunk Low Retro White Black Panda (Women's)
description: A women's shoe, the Wmns Dunk Low 'Black White' also known as ‘Panda’ emerges with a classic two-tone look. Built entirely with leather, the shoe's upper sports a white base overlaid by black, with black also marking the Swoosh branding. Perforations on the toe box provide breathability, while white branding appears on the tongue and heel patch. Underfoot, the two-tone rubber cupsole includes a concentric outsole to provide traction.

description: No description available.

description: No description available.

name: Nike Dunk Low Photon Dust (Women's)
description: The Wmns Dunk Low 'Photon Dust' brings a subdued look to its classic construction. Built entirely with leather, the shoe's upper appears with a white base, complemented by Photon Dust overlays, including on the Swoosh branding. The toe box includes perforations for breathability, while underfoot, the two-tone look continues onto the rubber cupsole that anchors the build, which includes a concentric outsole for traction.

name: Nike Dunk Low UNC (GS)
description: The Dunk Low GS 'University Blue' is a grade-school shoe with a two-tone look. Built entirely with leather, the shoe's upper appears in a mix of white and University Blue, with perforations on the toe box included for breathability. A nylon tongue and padded collar support the fit, while underfoot, a white midsole gives way to more University Blue on the outsole, which sports a concentric pattern for traction.

name: Nike Dunk Low Michigan State (GS)
description: Giving the nod to the Michigan State Spartans, the Dunk Low GS 'Michigan State' emerges in a team look. The shoe's upper is built with leather, finished in a mix of white and Team Green and supported by perforations on the toe box for breathability. A textile-lined collar and nylon tongue further bolster the design, while underfoot, a two-tone rubber cupsole includes a concentric outsole for traction.

name: Jordan 1 Low Wolf Grey (Women's)
description: The Women's Air Jordan 1 Low 'White Wolf Grey' features a white rubber midsole with cushioning and a translucent rubber outsole for support and style. The tongue features a silver Jumpman logo, and the back heel has a retro Wings logo. The white leather upper displays light grey accents and a matching Swoosh.

name: Jordan 2 Retro Low SP Off-White Black Blue
description: The Off-White x Air Jordan 2 Retro Low SP is Virgil Abloh's take on Michael Jordan's second signature shoe. The shoe's low-top construction is built with black leather on the upper, with the usual basketball-textured overlay appearing in tonal fashion. Royal blue accents the look, with exposed-foam marking the tongue, while a plastic zip tie, Helvetica text on the medial side and 'SHOELACES' on the laces bring signature Abloh features to the look. Underfoot, the midsole includes a crumbling aesthetic.

name: Jordan 4 Retro Red Thunder
description: Recalling the 'Thunder' colorway, the Air Jordan 4 Retro 'Red Thunder', also known as 'Crimson', emerges with similar color-blocking, albeit in a different mix of hues. The shoe's upper is built with a black nubuck base, highlighted by red throughout, including on the molded eyelets and quarter panel. More red marks the midsole, which includes visible Air for cushioning, while a two-tone rubber outsole is included for traction.

name: Nike Dunk Low Grey Fog
description: Delivering a subtle two-tone colorway of the classic silhouette originally released in 1985 is the Nike Dunk Low 'Grey Fog'. The all-leather upper features a white base with contrasting overlays in a light grey shade. The Swoosh, laces, and woven Nike tongue tag are in the same neutral tone. Additional Nike branding is on the heel tab and padded sockliner. On the bottom is a standard rubber cupsole that pairs white sidewalls with a grey rubber outsole.

description: No description available.

description: No description available.

name: Vans Sk8-Hi Horror Pack Nightmare on Elm Street Freddy Krueger
model: Horror Pack Nightmare on Elm Street Freddy Krueger
description: No description available.

name: Nike Blazer Low Off-White Black Electro Green
description: The Off-White x Nike Blazer Low 'Black' shoe reimagines a classic design by merging elements from Nike's rich history in basketball, trail running and skateboarding. Virgil Abloh collaborated with Nike’s design team to introduce an updated base that blends black vulcanized rubber and a TPU heel component influenced by the Air Terra Humara. The shoe's black leather upper features an additional bright green lacing system, circular cut-outs and distinctive Abloh touches, such as Helvetica text printed on the inner side and a plastic zip tie.

name: Jordan 1 Mid Armory Navy (GS)
description: The Air Jordan Mid GS 'Armory Navy' is a shoe available in big kid sizing that injects new energy to the classic silhouette via a refreshed color palette. The leather upper features a pristine white base, dark teal overlays, and a black mid-cut collar. It features a Jumpman icon on the woven tongue tag and a standard Wings logo stamped on the lateral ankle. It's built on a durable rubber cupsole with encapsulated Air-sole cushioning under the heel.

name: Nike Air Zoom Pegasus 38 Thunder Blue
description: No description available.

name: Vans Authentic 44 DX Bape 1st Camo
description: Combining the partner brands' signature design hallmark is the BAPE x Vans Authentic 44 DX 'First Camo.' BAPE's 1st Camo print, part of the capsule collection with the streetwear label, features woodland hues on Vans' traditional canvas upper built on a crisp white rubber midsole with a contrasting black foxing stripe. Inside is a crimson sockliner with dual BAPE and Vans branding with a matching red waffle-traction outsole.

name: Jordan 1 Retro High OG Patent Bred (GS)
description: The Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG GS 'Patent Bred' is a shoe made for older kids that delivers a glossy spin on the iconic OG colorway from 1985. Entirely made with patent leather, the upper features a black base with contrasting crimson accents on the toe box, Swoosh, and collar and heel overlays. Traditional branding elements are featured in the form of a woven Nike tongue tag and Wings logo that's stamped on the lateral ankle. The high-top is built on a sturdy rubber cupsole with encapsulated Air-sole cushioning in the heel.

name: adidas Superstar Core Black Cloud White Gold (GS)
description: No description available.

name: adidas Yeezy Boost 350 V2 Onyx
description: A monochromatic 'Onyx' hue envelops the latest Yeezy Boost 350 V2, the lifestyle runner from adidas and Kanye West. The upper features a dark black Primeknit weave along with rope laces, while a post-dyed monofilament side stripe can be found in a lighter black shade. A full-length Boost unit is encapsulated in a semi-translucent ribbed TPU midsole, while a black rubber outsole rounds out the look.

name: Jordan 1 Mid Diamond Shorts (GS)
description: Marking the diamond anniversary of the NBA, the Air Jordan 1 Mid SE GS ‘Diamond’ presents a low-key colorway on a hoops mid-top. The upper in white leather features contrasting black suede on the signature Swoosh, forefoot overlay and mid-cut collar. The ubiquitous Jumpman appears in a diamond on the tongue tag to symbolize the 75th anniversary of the league’s founding. Comfort and spring on the court are provided by the white midsole with an interior Air-sole unit in the heel atop a translucent rubber outsole.

name: adidas Yeezy Boost 350 V2 Bone
description: The adidas Yeezy Boost 350 V2 is treated to a monochromatic makeover. 'Bone' features an ivory Primeknit upper and a matching traditional lace closure. An off-white webbing pull tab at the heel and a see-through monofilament side stripe continue the tonal theme. Branding arrives in the form of a Three-Stripes logo on the interior heel and a Yeezy word mark stamped on the sockliner. A full-length TPU-wrapped Boost midsole provides responsive cushioning.

name: Nike Dunk Low Two-Toned Grey (GS)
description: No description available.

name: adidas Yeezy Foam RNR Onyx
description: Utilizing a sleek monochrome finish, the adidas Yeezy Foam Runner ‘Onyx’ is an understated colorway for a futuristic slip-on. A molded one-piece upper showcases open vents for breathability, while the injected EVA foam is lightweight and is secured by a unique traction pattern for grip.

name: Nike Air Max 270 Thunder Grey Total Orange
description: No description available.

name: ASICS Gel-1130 Black Graphite Grey
description: The ASICS Gel 1130 'Black' rolls out a black mesh upper with matching synthetic leather overlays and glossy tiger stripes. A black foam midsole contains shock-absorbing GEL heel inserts for a springy feel underfoot. The rubber outsole couples with ASICS' TRUSSTIC support system, a plastic shank for torsional rigidity.

name: Nike Air Force 1 Low Drake NOCTA Certified Lover Boy
description: Drake-inspired details imbue the NOCTA x Nike Air Force 1 Low ‘Certified Lover Boy’, an understated version of the unmistakable white-on-white AF1 colorway. Asymetric NOCTA and Nike Air branding on each heel tab ornament the white tumbled leather upper, with a nod to heritage details with a perforated toe box, variable width lacing and a low-cut padded collar. Drake's final wink is ‘Love You Forever’ inscribed in embossed lettering across the lateral sidewall of its white midsole, giving this classic a 2022 twist

name: Nike Air Force 1 Mid Off-White Black
description: Celebrating the 40th anniversary of the Air Force 1, Nike works with Off-White on an AF1 Mid. The upper is crafted with black textile, while traditional Off-White flourishes can be seen on the shoe, including an overlay of secondary lacing and an orange zip-tie. A graffiti style 'AIR' appears on the tongue, while signature helvetica text can be found on the medial side. The wavy midsole showcases an orange tinted visible Air unit, while the outsole gets reworked with nubby multicolor spikes.

name: Nike Air Force 1 Mid Off-White White
description: Carrying on the visionary legacy of Virgil Abloh, Nike works with Off-White on a new take of the Air Force 1 Mid. Crafted with a white textile upper, signature Off-White cues can be seen across the shoe including a set of secondary laces, helvetica text on the medial side, and an orange zip-tie. The midsole goes from smooth to wavy, highlighted by an orange-tinted visible Air unit in the heel. The outsole gets reworked with multicolor rubber spike nubs, placed at the middle and toe area. New details on the mid include a graffiti style "AIR" on the tongue and translucent Swooshes on the side profiles.

name: Nike Air Force 1 Mid Off-White Pine Green
description: With ancillary lacing woven through Flywire cables, orange tags on the Swoosh and hanging zip-tie tag, the Off-White x Nike Air Force 1 Mid SP Leather ‘Pine Green’ is a fitting tribute to the original design language of Virgil Abloh. The leather upper in kelly green is supported on a white midsole with a visible Airsole unit in the heel, while the topline undulates above a bristled green rubber outsole. Branding pops in white with Swooshes embellished with tonal crisscross stitching, 'AIR' tongue stitching and alternating lateral heel illustrations of a candelabra on the left and ‘OFF’ on the right.

name: Nike Free RN 2018 Thunder Blue Gunsmoke
description: No description available.

name: adidas Yeezy Foam RNR Onyx (Kids)
description: With a design ahead of its time, the adidas Yeezy Foam Runner Kids ‘Onyx’ gives the low-key clog a noir treatment. With only subtle branding limited to an adidas logo on the outsole, the flair comes from the all-black molded upper in injected EVA foam featuring eye-catching vent throughout the vamp and a wavy pattern at the sole that offers multi-surface traction. A soft and textured top layer gives the footbed step-in comfort.

name: Converse Chuck Taylor All Star 70 Hi Stussy Black
make: Converse Chuck Taylor All Star 70 Hi
description: A heritage favorite gets a noir makeover with the Stussy x Converse Chuck 70 Hi ‘Black.’ The upper is constructed from black hemp, the lateral ankle adorned with a stitched Star logo with only the outer circle of the white All-Star badge stitched on the reverse side. Underfoot, the high-top is supported by a rubber midsole in white with pinstriping and unvarnished sidewalls. The interior tongue and diminutive heel tag display Stussy branding.

name: Saucony Shadow 6000 Stoney Creek
description: No description available.

name: Nike Dunk Low Triple Pink (GS)
description: The Dunk Low GS 'Triple Pink' also known as 'Barbie' updates the traditional design of the vintage Nike basketball shoe. The sneaker goes against the traditional two-tone color blocking with an all-leather upper in light pink for both the base and overlays. Hot pink highlights Nike branding along the Swoosh, tongue tag, and heel. While the rubber outsole secures the build, a breathable nylon tongue gives comfort.

name: Jordan 1 Retro High OG Taxi (GS)
description: Replicating the hues of the 2018 ‘Bred Toe,’ the Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG GS ‘Yellow Toe’ is a big kids’ shoe presented with standout color blocking. A Taxi yellow toe box pairs with overlays at the heel and forefoot in black contrasting against white quarter panels. A traditional cupsole with an interior Air-sole unit provides support underfoot. The lateral ankle displays a retro Wings logo while ‘Nike Air’ appears on the tongue tag.

name: Jordan 3 Retro Fire Red (2022) (GS)
description: The Air Jordan 3 Retro GS 'Fire Red' returns in a 2022 edition designed for big kids and showcasing one of the original four colorways of this heritage classic. The upper appears in white tumbled leather upper, accompanied by the signature elephant-print overlays adorning the forefoot and heel. Scarlet accents bring vibrant pops of color to the Jumpman icon embroidered on the tongue and the Nike Air branding embossed on the heel tab, and the shoe features molded eyelets and a perforated leather collar. Adding a final touch of flair, the polyurethane midsole is adorned with a splash of Fire Red, accentuating the visible Air-sole unit nestled in the heel for cushioning and comfort.

name: Jordan 1 Retro High OG Chicago Lost and Found (GS)
description: The signature 'Chicago' colorway is revisited in this high-top made for big kids. The Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG GS ‘Lost & Found’ receives a distressed look on the white leather in the upper and the padded collar. Pops of color are delivered with the 'Nike Air' tongue tag, bright red overlays and laces and Swoosh in black. The shoe is supported on a cupsole in white rubber with a bright red outsole and white sidewalls. The ankle flap features branding with the classic Jordan Wings logo.

name: Jordan 1 Mid Ice Blue (2022) (GS)
description: No description available.

name: Jordan 4 Retro Midnight Navy (GS)
description: The Air Jordan 4 Retro GS 'Midnight Navy' showcases the timeless details that made the original design iconic in 1989 and is available in extended sizing for older kids. The classic silhouette features an upper in white tumbled leather, accentuated by a Jumpman-branded heel tab with a speckled grey finish and navy molded eyelets. Enhanced support is supplied by the matching grey wings provide, while quarter panel netting enhances comfortable ventilation. On the tongue, a Fire Red Flight logo accompanies a woven Jumpman tag. The PU midsole provides lightweight cushioning with its visible Air-sole unit in the heel.

name: adidas Yeezy Boost 350 V2 Carbon Beluga
description: The adidas Yeezy Boost 350 V2 ‘Carbon Beluga’ combines bold hues with a striking pattern. The dark grey upper in Primeknit, featuring black waves and orange speckles, is secured by rope laces. The lateral side showcases a bright orange stripe with the ‘SPLY-350’ branding. The sneaker offers a comfortable experience with its full-length Boost midsole and a supportive TPU cage. The design is finished with a robust rubber outsole.

name: ASICS Gel-NYC Oyster Grey
description: The ASICS Gel NYC 'Cream Oyster Grey' presents an off-white mesh upper with suede and synthetic leather overlays in multiple shades of grey. ASICS' spiral logo decorates the tongue, while the 'GEL' signoff adorns the heel. A bicolor midsole contains GEL inserts in the forefoot and heel for a plush sensation underfoot. Pods on the rubber outsole make way for traction segments for a surefooted experience.

name: ASICS Gel-NYC Graphite Grey Black
description: No description available.

name: Jordan 5 Retro UNC University Blue
description: The Tar Heels’ school colors are honored in the Air Jordan 5 Retro SE ‘UNC.’ With shark-tooth details on the black midsole, the University Blue nubuck leather upper is complemented by breathable netting at the quarter panel. The tongue is adorned with a stitched Jumpman in reflective silver. Support and traction underfoot are supplied by a PU midsole in black with an exposed Air-sole unit in the heel atop a herringbone-patterned clear outsole. a translucent herringbone-traction outsole.

name: Nike Air Terra Forma Off-White Wheat Green Strike
description: The Off-White x Nike Air Terra Forma ‘Wheat’ takes a heritage hiking shoe of the late ‘80s and early ‘90s and treats it to a reinvention by a legendary designer. With black rubber outsoles outfitted with oversized spikes, the midsole with an exposed Max Air unit appears in an array of melded orange, blue, pink and pale green. A zippered cover on the neon green tongue reveals a shape evoking the Air Jordan 6, one of the late Virgil Abloh’s favorite models, while a clear stitched Swoosh adorns the upper. The outsole declares ‘Tread Lightly’ in exaggerated block letters.

name: Jordan 1 Retro High OG Spider-Man Across the Spider-Verse (GS)
description: Inspired by the animated Spiderverse film featuring Marvel Comics Spiderman character Miles Morales, the Marvel x Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG GS ‘Next Chapter' is a shoe available in grade-school sizing. The shoe design follows the classic silhouette and color scheme, but with a modern update that includes a white leather upper and black patent leather on the Swoosh and high-cut collar. The contrasting crimson overlays are made up of different textures and prints and arranged in a patchwork style that represents the Spider-Verse’s various dimensions. The sneaker is anchored by a vintage off-white midsole and a red semi-clear rubber outsole. The shoe also features classic OG-inspired branding, such as a Nike tag on the tongue and the Wings logo on the lateral ankle.

name: Jordan 4 Retro SE Craft Photon Dust (GS)
colorway: Photon Dust/Pale Vanilla/Off White/Grey Fog/Flat Pewter/Sail
description: The Air Jordan 4 Retro SE Craft GS ‘Photon Dust’ is a neutral-toned sneaker designed for big kids. The white foam midsole is enhanced with an exposed Air-sole unit and supported by a two-tone rubber outsole with herringbone-patterned traction.

name: adidas Campus 00s Core Black
description: The adidas Campus 00s 'Core Black Gum' rocks extra-wide laces to secure the black suede upper. Contrasting white accents land on the serrated leather three-stripes and collar lining. A gold foil 'Campus' print sits above the aforementioned, while the Trefoil adorns the tongue and back tab. These shoes have off-white sidewalls that pair perfectly with a herringbone-patterned, gum rubber outsole.

name: Saucony 3D Grid Hurricane Bodega
description:
The Saucony 3D Grid Hurricane Bodega is an athletic shoe that features white mesh, green suede, quilted metallic woven fabric, and brown leather. Iridescent Violet Saucony Creek branding appears on the sides. A Sculptural White midsole is accented by striped panels and a gum outsole. Saucony branding appears on the rear, while Bodega Grid branding adorns the tongue.

Bodega is a Boston-based sneaker boutique founded in 2006 that is widely considered to have placed Boston on the streetwear map. Known for securing rare shoe releases and collaborations with brands on sneaker designs, Bodega has teamed up with Boston-based Saucony again, a partnership they have explored a few times since initially collaborating in 2008.

In our opinion, the best feature of the 3D Grid Hurricane is its appealing mix of patterns, which come together to create one coherent aesthetic. The Saucony 3D Grid Hurricane Bodega released on January 21, 2023, and retailed at $150.

name: Nike Zoom Vomero 5 Photon Dust Metallic Silver (Women's)
description: The Nike Women's Air Zoom Vomero 5 'Photon Dust Metallic Silver' is an old-school runner designed for long-lasting comfort and adorned with sparkling details. The upper is made of a combination of breathable mesh and synthetic leather in a sleek light grey hue. The toe box and iconic Swoosh are embellished with glossy chrome accents while the molded heel cage provides a stable and supportive fit. The shoe is equipped with a foam midsole with responsive forefoot and heel Zoom Air cushioning.

name: Jordan 4 Retro Thunder (2023)
description: The 2023 Air Jordan 4 Retro 'Thunder' reintroduces the popular color scheme that was first released in 2006 and later reissued in 2012. The shoe's upper appears in all-black nubuck with yellow accents on the molded eyelets, lower tongue and quarter panel, the latter two draped with black netting. Cushioned comfort underfoot is supplied by a yellow PU midsole and is enhanced by the heel’s exposed Air-sole unit. The Flight tongue tag and molded heel tab bear the iconic Jumpman branding.

name: Jordan 3 Retro White Cement Reimagined (GS)
description: The Air Jordan 3 Retro GS 'White Cement Reimagined' is a shoe design that is available in grade school sizes that brings back the beloved original color scheme of the classic silhouette. The upper is crafted using pristine white leather, with gray elephant print overlays that are modeled after the distinctive design from 1988. The polyurethane midsole has a vintage finish and comes with an encapsulated Air-sole unit in the forefoot, as well as an exposed unit in the heel. The white leather tongue is adorned with a stitched crimson Jumpman logo, and the pre-yellowed back tab features embossed Nike Air branding.

name: ASICS Gel-1130 White Midnight (Women's)
description: The ASICS Women's Gel 1130 'White Midnight' dons a white mesh upper with matching synthetic leather overlays that have a touch of metallic silver. Navy side stripes match the mesh collar lining. An off-white EVA midsole contains GEL inserts in the heel, coupled with ASICS' TRUSSTIC support system for midfoot stability.

name: ASICS Gel-Kayano 14 White Midnight (Women's)
description: The ASICS Women's Gel Kayano 14 'White Midnight' dons a white open-cell mesh upper, bolstered with cream and silver-hued synthetic leather overlays. Heavy dark grey lines form the tiger stripes, while the ASICS logo adorns the tongue and insoles. A GEL heel unit on the foam midsole provides shock absorption with every step.

name: Jordan 4 Retro Thunder (2023) (GS)
description: The Air Jordan 4 Retro GS ‘Thunder’ 2023 edition is designed for older kids and features the popular two-tone colorway that first appeared in 2006. The black nubuck upper is accented with bold yellow details that adorn the molded eyelets, quarter panel, and lower tongue. The quarter panel and tongue are also constructed with black netting, harking back to the AJ4’s original design in 1989. The molded back tab and woven tongue tag display classic Jumpman branding. The sneaker is built on a yellow polyurethane midsole that incorporates exposed Air-sole cushioning and is reinforced by a herringbone-patterned rubber outsole for improved grip.

Durable synthetic overlays arrive in a striking metallic silver. A lightweight EVA midsole with visible Gel cushioning in the forefoot and heel offers optimal comfort. name: Jordan 7 Retro White Infrared (GS)
description: The Air Jordan 7 Retro GS 'White Infrared' is designed for older children and borrows inspiration from an original Air Jordan 6 colorway. The shoe's upper unit is made of white leather with perforated details for ventilation, while an interior bootie is crafted from black neoprene material. The Infrared Jumpman icon is stitched onto the lateral collar, providing a pop of color. The shoe's polyurethane midsole is colored with the same vibrant hue and features encapsulated Air-sole cushioning. The translucent rubber outsole reinforces the midsole, giving the shoe a finished look.

name: Jordan 1 Retro High OG SP Union LA Bephies Beauty Supply Summer of ‘96
model: Union LA Bephies Beauty Supply Summer of ‘96
description: The Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG SP collaboration among Union LA, Bephie’s Beauty Supply, and Jordan Brand, offers a fresh take on the classic silhouette. It features a white leather upper with exposed stitching in green, woven detailing inspired by the Nike Air Footscape Woven and a grey Swoosh. The shoe's traditional lines are accented with yellow trim and match the laces and a discreet 'UN/LA' label on the lateral ankle. Branding appears via a tonal Wings logo on the collar flap and a woven Nike Air tongue tag. Underfoot, the durable rubber cupsole has a vintage pre-yellowed finish, adding to the retro vibe.

name: Jordan 4 Retro Red Cement (GS)
description: The Air Jordan 4 Retro GS 'Red Cement' for big kids blends the classic color blocking with a recognizable palette inspired by Chicago. Breathable netting appears on the quarter panel of the white leather upper and is contrasted by black molded eyelets. The sneaker is equipped with a two-tone polyurethane midsole, housing visible Air-sole cushioning and reinforced by a rubber outsole with herringbone traction pattern. The distinctive support wings of the shoe are adorned with crimson accents and speckled black detailing, matching the Jumpman logo on the heel tag. Another Jumpman logo is present on the Flight tongue tag.

name: Nike Air Force 1 Mid SP Off-White Varsity Maize
description: The Off-White x Nike Air Force 1 Mid SP Leather 'Varsity Maize' gives a modern twist to the classic design. The upper is made of white and yellow leather and displays a white Swoosh with zigzag stitching. Traditional laces are paired with an added lacing system through exposed Flywire cables. It has a wavy sole with visible air cushioning and a rubber spiked bottom. A grim reaper graphic adorns the lateral side and the medial side displays Off-White text.

The shoe features a full-length Boost midsole encased in a ribbed TPU cage which is supported by a grippy rubber outsole. description: The Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG GS 'UNC Toe' has been created with older kids in mind and displays a color palette that pays homage to Michael Jordan's alma mater. Supporting the sneaker is a white rubber midsole, equipped with encapsulated Air-sole cushioning for optimal comfort. The midsole is accompanied by a grippy rubber outsole in Tar Heel blue, ensuring traction and stability. The upper is crafted from smooth leather, featuring a balanced combination of white and black, while the toe box, heel overlay, and ankle areas are adorned with hits of University Blue. The shoe's design is completed with a woven Nike tongue tag and an embossed Wings logo on the lateral collar flap which evoke the OG-inspired aesthetic.

name: adidas Gazelle Indoor Bliss Pink Purple (Women's)
description: The adidas Women's Gazelle 'Bliss Pink Purple' has a textured pink suede upper with a bolstered T-toe overlay and a purple leather back tab. Black serrated leather three-stripes adorn the side, accompanied by a debossed 'Gazelle' wordmark. An embossed Trefoil stands alone on the tongue tag. These shoes have a partially see-through gum rubber sole unit.

name: adidas Yeezy Boost 350 V2 Steel Grey
description: Made from a stretchy Primeknit upper, the adidas Yeezy Boost 350 V2 'Steel Grey' sports distinct center stitching and a near see-through side stripe. The sock-like build also has a heel pull to make it easy to put on your shoes or take them off. A full-length Boost midsole is wrapped in a ribbed cage that keeps their monochromatic vibe.

name: Nike Dunk Low Cacao Wow (Women's)
description: The Nike Women's Dunk Low 'Cacao Wow' showcases an upper crafted from smooth leather, combining a crisp white base with rich chocolate brown overlays that extend to the iconic Swoosh logo. The midsole boasts a vintage off-white finish and houses an interior foam wedge, providing lightweight cushioning and support. The brown rubber outsole offers durability and traction for everyday wear. Old-school Nike branding can be found on the tongue tag, back tab, and sockliner.

name: Jordan 4 Retro Metallic Gold (Women's)
description: The Women’s Air Jordan 4 Retro ‘Metallic Gold’ has a smooth leather upper with a subtle off-white finish and metallic gold eyelets for a regal look. These shoes have a breathable quarter panel netting and a debossed Jumpman logo on the tongue. The prominent molded heel tab backs a plush collar. Underneath, a soft midsole reveals an Air-sole heel unit for soft cushioning. The classic herringbone rubber outsole provides traction and optimal grip.

name: Jordan 1 Retro High OG Satin Bred (Women's)
description: Paying homage to a highly exclusive AJ1 release from 2016, the Women's Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG 'Satin Bred' is adorned in the iconic black and red color combination, delivered in all-over shiny satin. Drawing inspiration from the original design, it features classic branding details such as a woven Nike tag on the tongue and an embroidered Wings logo on the lateral collar flap. The sneaker is supported by a contrasting white midsole, which incorporates an encapsulated Air-sole unit in the heel for cushioning, while a crimson rubber outsole provides reliable traction on various surfaces.

name: Jordan 4 Retro Military Blue (2024)
description: Bringing back a classic OG colorway, the 2024 version of the Jordan 4 Retro 'Military Blue' also known as 'Industrial Blue' returns with an off-white leather upper and nubuck forefoot overlays. The blue Jumpman logo decorates the tongue tag, matching the color of the molded eyelets, back tab and the underneath of the side panel netting. These shoes have a lightweight midsole with an encapsulated Air-sole forefoot unit and a visible Air bag in the heel.

name: Nike Zoom Vomero 5 Pink Foam Team Red (Women's)
description: The women's Nike Air Zoom Vomero 5 'Pink Foam Team Red' blends synthetic leather overlays in a soft pastel pink against a breathable maroon mesh upper. Rearfoot support is ensured by a molded heel counter and the quarter panel is reinforced with a TPU cage for midfoot stability. Enhancing responsiveness and energy rebound, the foam midsole features embedded Zoom Air cushioning.

name: Jordan 4 Retro Vivid Sulfur (Women's)
description: The Women's Air Jordan 4 Retro 'Vivid Sulfur' brings some of the signature AJ4 details like a breathable side netting and support wings for midfoot support. The smooth white leather upper gets contrasting yellow accents on the eyelets, lining, and Jumpman logos on the tongue and back tab. These shoes have a two-tone midsole, equipped with an exposed Air-sole unit inside the heel.

name: Jordan 1 Retro High OG Latte (Women's)
description: The Women's Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG 'Latte’ sits on an off-white rubber midsole with an Air-sole heel unit enclosed in a lightweight polyurethane wedge for comfort. The leather upper in clean white features the signature Swoosh and forefoot overlay in black, with the heel and collar flap arriving in dark tan. The latter displays the iconic Wings logo, and the tongue is adorned by a Nike Air tag.

name: Jordan 11 Retro Low Diffused Blue (GS)
description: Combining a ballistic mesh upper with a shiny patent leather overlay, the Air Jordan 11 Retro Low GS 'Diffused Blue' is adorned with a stylized '23' on the back tab, as well as a Jumpman logo on the tongue and heel. These shoes have a white Phylon midsole that pairs with full-length Air-sole cushioning. Underfoot, the see-through outsole is fitted with herringbone-style pods and a visible carbon fiber shank plate to keep the midfoot stable.

name: Nike Kobe 8 Protro Mambacita (GS)
description: The Nike Kobe 8 GS ‘Mambacita’ pays tribute to the legacy that Kobe Bryant's daughter, ‘Gigi’ built with her dad. The engineered mesh upper is surrounded by an allover butterfly print, adorned with a metallic gold Swoosh. ‘Gigi’ is stamped on the left heel, while her jersey No. 2 appears on the right heel. A drop-in React foam midsole keeps every step lightweight, while a herringbone-style rubber outsole provides smooth traction underfoot.

name: Nike Shox TL White Metallic Silver Max Orange (Women's)
description: The Nike Women's Shox TL 'White Silver' 2023 utilizes an upper in a textured white mesh reinforced by matching TPU overlays. The metallic silver molded Swoosh is stitched and intriguing color pops arrive in the form of Max Orange Nike Shox branding adorning both the tongue and the rear heel. The shoe's foundation rests on a robust rubber outsole while a series of polyurethane Shox pillars provide innovative cushioning.

name: Jordan 4 Retro SE Craft Medium Olive (GS)
description: The Air Jordan 4 Retro SE Craft GS in 'Olive' features an upper made from layers of nubuck and suede, with side panels in embossed suede in a grid pattern, replacing the original TPU netting. Contrasting black details arrive on the leather support wings, molded eyelets, and the lining inside the collar. The shoe has a lightweight foam midsole with visible Air-sole cushioning. The tongue tag and a semi-transparent tab at the back display cream-colored Jumpman logos.

name: ASICS Gel-1130 Black Pure Silver

Metallic silver pops accentuate the tiger stripes, toe wrap and heel overlay. Grey knit lines the collar, keeping the subtle palette. A black midsole contains a shock-absorbing GEL heel insert for a soft ride.

The PU midsole has a visible Air-sole unit in the heel for added comfort.

name: Nike Air Foamposite One Galaxy (2025)
description: The 2025 version of the Nike Air Foamposite One 'Galaxy' originally released during NBA All-Star Weekend in 2012. These shoes have a nebular design, using blue and purple throughout the molded Foamposite upper. Black nubuck stars on the collar and eyestay, touched with an embroidered mini-Swoosh on the forefoot. A glow-in-the-dark, see-through rubber outsole keeps every step true.

The upper mixes contrasting black pops on the mesh collar and nubuck eyestay. An embroidered mini-Swoosh adorns the forefoot, while Penny Hardaway’s logo appears on the tongue and the back of the heel. These shoes have full-length Zoom Air cushioning for a soft feel underfoot and a carbon fiber spring plate to promote stability.

The tongue and the heel pull tab display Jumpman logos.

name: Nike Air Max 180 Ultramarine (2024)
description: A throwback to a '90s OG classic, the 2024 iteration of the Nike Air Max 180 ‘Ultramarine’ combines white textile with off-white suede overlays on an upper accented by a blue leather Swoosh. The tongue tag, back heel and heel counter arrive in red accents for a subtle pop. These shoes provide 180 degrees of visible Air cushioning, bonded to the outsole for a seamless feel underfoot.

name: Saucony Grid Shadow 2 Jae Tips What's the Occasion? Wear To The Party
model: Jae Tips What's the Occasion? Wear To The Party
description: The Jae Tips x Saucony Grid Shadow 2 ‘Wear to the Party’ celebrates the partners’ second collaborative effort: ‘What’s the Occasion?' These shoes have an airy off-white mesh upper contrasted by Saucony’s green logo, a pink nubuck midfoot overlay and hairy brown suede wavy lines around the mudguard. A tan EVA midsole and a pink rubber outsole round out the look. A ‘Forever’ signoff on the side of the forefoot is accompanied by ‘Savior,' Jae Tips’ floral motif on the back of the heel; and a theme ‘Wear to the Party’ printed on the left sockliner.

These shoes have a durable rubber cupsole that contrasts the white sidewalls and a crimson outsole.

name: Jordan 1 Retro Low OG Mocha (GS)
description: Taking design cues from the 'Dark Mocha' originally released in 2020, the Air Jordan 1 Retro Low OG GS ‘Mocha’ features a white leather upper with contrasting black accents on the Swoosh and forefoot overlay. Brown nubuck accents on the heel and back tab give them a solid contrast. These shoes have a standard rubber cupsole with stitched sidewalls and encapsulated Air-sole cushioning for a plush feel.

name: Jordan 12 Retro Taxi Flip (GS)
description: The Air Jordan 12 Retro GS ‘Taxi Flip’ is inspired by the original 1996 design. These shoes have a white tumbled leather upper, lizard-textured mudguard and stitched lines. The midfoot overlay and Jumpman logo on the tongue give them a splash of red to liven up the look. A lightweight Phylon midsole is fitted with Zoom Air cushioning for a smooth and responsive sensation.

name: UGG Disquette Slipper Chestnut (Women's)
description:
The UGG Disquette Slipper Chestnut W is footwear sized for women (W) that come with plush lining and a thick outsole.

This slipper features a soft upper in a chestnut brown colorway with a rounded toe, a raised center seam, and heat-embossed UGG branding on the lateral side. This model has a sheepskin insole with a branding patch and a sheepskin collar and lining. The 1-inch platform outsole is constructed from Treadlite by UGG as well as EVA. Recycled polyester fibers bind this slipper together.

The UGG Disquette Slipper Chestnut W was released in January 2021 at a retail price of $100.

make: UGG Classic Ultra Mini Platform Boot
description:
The UGG Classic Ultra Mini Platform Black W is an addition to the women's collection by UGG, available in a black pattern.

This shoe features an asymmetrical topline upper constructed with sheepskin and soft suede. 17mm UGGplush, which comprises 80% wool and 20% lyocell, is used on the interior lining. Other details include a heel pull tab, overlock stitch detailing on the exterior, and a leather heel label with the UGG logo. A 3.5" shaft height and 2 inches platform supported by an EVA midsole and Treadlite outsole complete the design. 

The UGG Classic Ultra Mini Platform Black W was released on October 10th, 2022. Initially, it retailed at $150.

name: ASICS GEL-Kayano 14 Cream Sweet Pink
description: The ASICS Gel Kayano 14 'Cream Sweet Pink' brings an open-cell mesh upper touched with shiny, silver synthetic leather overlays. Bold black lines trace the contours of the side stripes, while contrasting pink pops decorate the logos on the tongue and heel. A white foam midsole gets a hot pink GEL unit for a plush feel underfoot. The rubber outsole uses flex grooves for a springy ride and an exposed TRUSSTIC system to contain the midfoot.

name: ASICS Gel-1130 White Black
description: The ASICS Gel 1130 'White Black' couples a white ventilated mesh with matching synthetic leather overlays. Bold black side stripes match the heel wrap and ASICS tongue tag. The foam midsole contains an exposed GEL heel insert for a plush feel. The black rubber outsole contains a plastic shank, known as the TRUSSTIC support system, enhancing midfoot stability.

name: UGG Classic Ultra Mini Chestnut (Kids)
description:
The UGG Classic Ultra Mini Chestnut (Kids) applies the ultra-short UGG Classic Mini silhouette to a kid-sized model.

What makes this UGG Classic Ultra Mini shoe stand out is the warm Chestnut colorway and the ultra-low boot shaft height. Like the UGG Classic, the Ultra Mini was designed with comfort in mind. The primary lining is made of plush, high-quality sheepskin, while the UGGplush Lining uses a combination of upcycled wool, Tencel, and/or recycled fibers. The outsole is crafted from soft foam, adding cushioning without weighing the shoe down. To further UGG’s sustainability goals, at least 40 percent of the shoe’s material comes from recycled or renewable sources.

Our experts like that the upper is made from pre-treated suede. This means it repels a small amount of water and will last longer than untreated materials. The UGG Classic Ultra Mini Chestnut (Kids) was released on January 27, 2023, and retailed at $110.

name: Jordan Jumpman Jack TR Travis Scott University Red
description: The Jordan Jumpman Jack TR 'University Red' sparks Travis Scott's debut signature sneakers with a black canvas upper, accented by an off-white midfoot strap and tumbled leather overlays. A red Jumpman logo adorns the tongue, jelling with the reverse suede Swoosh on the side. The Cactus Jack face logo stands out on the heel area, while an oversized 'Jack' is inscribed in red, contrasting the cream-colored rubber outsole.

name: Saucony Grid Shadow 2 Bodega Jaunt Woven
description:
The Saucony Grid Shadow 2 Bodega Jaunt Woven is an eclectic, layered shoe that represents a collaboration between Saucony footwear and the Bodega streetwear brand.

The Bodega x Saucony Grid Shadow 2 Jaunt Woven features an upper constructed primarily of hemp and cotton in beige and light brown tones. Dark green textile forms a mudguard overlaid with patterned textile in a light brown. A Saucony Swoosh undulates across the side panel in a Creamy Mocha color, while a Lime Green Swoosh hits the lateral toecap. An off-white EVA foam midsole provides cushioning and springy energy return, while the recycled gum rubber outsole in Speckled Brown, orange, off-white, and Lime Green provides a dependable grip.

What we enjoy most about this sneaker are all the hits of bright branding, particularly the dual branding on the tongue, with "Bodega" in bright Lime Green and a Saucony Swoosh in orange red. The Saucony Grid Shadow 2 Bodega Jaunt Woven was released on February 23, 2024, for a retail price of $140.

name: Nike Air Terra Humara Undefeated Light Menta
description: The Undefeated x Nike Air Terra Humara 'Light Menta' dons a grey mesh upper, contrasted with bright teal overlays comprised of leather, suede and TPU. The midfoot overlay gets a reflective coating, which is built into the lacing system for a snug fit. The Undefeated's 'Play Dirty' tagline is stamped on the collar, while the Five Strike logo is displayed on the heel tab and tongue. These sneakers have a speckled midsole fitted with an exposed Air-sole heel unit for a plush feel.

name: Jordan 3 Retro OG Black Cement (2024)
description: The 2024 version of the Air Jordan 3 Retro OG 'Black Cement' stays true to the 1988 original, rolling out a black tumbled leather upper with grey elephant print forefoot and heel overlays. An embroidered red Jumpman stars on the tongue, while a raised Nike Air logo adorns the heel. A white foam midsole equips Air-sole cushioning, adding a touch of black along the heel, anchored by a grey rubber outsole.

name: Jordan 3 Retro Black Cement (2024) (GS)
description: The 2024 iteration of the Air Jordan 3 Retro OG GS 'Black Cement' brings a tumbled black leather upper complemented by grey elephant print overlays on the forefoot and heel. A red Jumpman contrasts the grey leather tongue, while the heel panel shows a raised Nike Air logo. Black touches on the midsole heel reveal an exposed Air-sole unit underfoot.

description: No description available.

name: Jordan 12 Retro Blueberry
description: The Air Jordan 12 Retro 'Blueberry' brings sunrise-style stitch lines on a white tumbled leather upper, accented with lizard-patterned blue overlays. The Jumpman logo adorns the tongue and heel tab for a signature touch. The Phylon midsole equips a full-length Zoom Air unit, riding on a blue rubber outsole aided by a carbon fiber shank plate for stability.

name: Jordan 12 Retro Blueberry (GS)
description: Made for grade schoolers, the Air Jordan 12 Retro GS 'Blueberry' rocks a white tumbled leather upper tooled with radiating stitch lines and contrasting lizard-like overlays. Black knit lines the collar, matching the Jumpman logo embroidered on the tongue. A blue outsole with herringbone traction pods works with an exposed carbon fiber shank plate for enhanced stability.

name: Jordan 4 Retro Fear (2024)
description: The 2024 edition of the Air Jordan 4 Retro 'Fear' brings back the 2013 colorway, using a nubuck upper accented with a grey mudguard and toe wrap. White molded eyelets match the Jumpman logos on the tongue tag and heel. White speckles decorate the a black foam midsole, which packs an exposed Air-Sole heel unit.

name: Jordan 4 Retro Fear (2024) (GS)
description: The Air Jordan 4 Retro GS 'Fear' stays loyal to the 2013 version, bringing a black nubuck upper accented with grey and silver details. The Jumpman logo graces the tongue tag, matching the white molded eyelets and collar lining. Another Jumpman logo can be found on the molded heel panel, matching the speckled details on the black foam midsole.

name: adidas Handball Spezial Earth Strata Gum (Women's)
description: Brought back from the '70s archive, the adidas Women's Handball Spezial 'Earth Strata Gum' has an upper crafted from brown hairy suede, contrasted by white leather touches on the back tab and serrated three-stripes. Synthetic leather lines the collar, while the tongue is adorned with an 'adidas Handball Spezial' tag. A gum rubber sole unit completes the look.

name: Nike Kobe 5 Protro X-Ray
description: The Nike Zoom Kobe 5 Protro 'X-Ray' sports a glow-in-the-dark X-ray graphic resembling the bones of the foot. A deep royal blue synthetic upper works with a padded mesh collar and integrated Flywire cables for lockdown. A lightweight Cushlon midsole contains a responsive Zoom Air forefoot unit, while a blue see-through rubber outsole glows in the dark.

name: Jordan 3 Retro OG SP A Ma Maniére While You Were Sleeping (Women's)
model: A Ma Maniére While You Were Sleeping (Women's)
description: The A Ma Maniére x Women's Air Jordan 3 Retro 'While You Were Sleeping' mixes a black tumbled leather upper with grey hairy suede forefoot and heel overlays. Perforated violet ore nubuck hits adorn the eyestay and quilted satin-lined collar, which is stripped of padding. A slimmed down tongue alternates the luxury brand's 'A' logo next to the iconic Jumpman logo, while a raised Nike Air logo graces the heel tab. A vintage off-white foam midsole packs an exposed Air-sole heel unit for a plush feel underfoot.

name: Nike Kobe 5 X-Ray (GS)
description: The Nike Zoom Kobe 5 GS 'X-Ray' rocks a blue synthetic upper, including a glow-in-the-dark X-ray graphic that looks like a skeletal foot. Kobe Bryant's logo adorns the tongue, while his signature graces the heel. The foam midsole equips a springy Zoom Air forefoot unit for a responsive feel. A blue see-through rubber outsole glows in the dark for that eye-catching style.

name: Jordan 11 Retro Legend Blue (2024)
description: Originally released in 1996, the 2024 edition of the Air Jordan 11 Retro 'Legend Blue / Columbia' sports a white leather upper, accented with a matching patent leather mudguard and contrasted with a Columbia Blue embroidered Jumpman right below the collar. Bold black accents are carefully-placed in the back tab and collar lining. A white Phylon midsole partners with an Air-sole unit to bring you a lightweight feel underfoot. An icy, see-through rubber outsole showcases a carbon fiber shank plate to keep the midfoot stable.

name: Jordan 4 Retro OG SP A Ma Maniére While You Were Sleeping (Women's)
model: A Ma Maniére While You Were Sleeping (Women's)
description: The A Ma Maniére x Women's Air Jordan 4 Retro 'While You Were Sleeping' takes a grey leather upper and adds matching suede forefoot overlays and a deconstructed knit collar. Iconic details like the quarter-panel netting, molded eyelets and prominent support wings are kept intact. The Jumpman and A Ma Maniére logos take turns on each tongue tag, while a raised Nike Air logo graces the heel. A two-tone midsole boasts an exposed Air-sole heel unit for a plush feel underfoot.

name: Jordan 1 Retro Low OG SP Travis Scott Medium Olive
description: The Travis Scott x Jordan 1 Retro Low OG SP 'Reverse Olive / Medium Olive' dons a green suede base with chalk white leather overlays on the forefoot and heel areas. Scott's black tumbled leather reverse Swoosh adorns the side, while red pops touch the Nike Air tongue as well as the Wings and Cactus Jack logos on the back tab. These sneakers have an off-white midsole, reinforced by a sturdy olive rubber outsole.

name: Jordan 4 Retro Oxidized Green (GS)
description: The Air Jordan 4 Retro GS 'Oxidized Green' has a white leather upper, including support wings and heel tab. The latter gets a dark green Jumpman logo, matching the collar lining, netted quarter panel and plastic eyelets. The Jumpman logo appears again on the insoles and tongue. These shoes have a dual-tone foam midsole, equipped with an exposed Air-sole heel unit and anchored by a light grey rubber outsole.

name: Nike Kobe 8 Protro Lakers Away
description: The Nike Kobe 8 Protro 'Lakers Away' rocks a black engineered mesh upper with matching no-sew overlays and a gold embroidered Swoosh. Kobe Bryant's purple sheath logo is stamped on the tongue and heel. A drop-in React foam midsole takes the place of the Lunarlon foam undergirding the original Kobe 8. A herringbone-traction rubber outsole exposes a bottom-loaded carbon fiber shank plate for midfoot stability.

name: Nike Kobe 8 Protro University Red
description: The Nike Kobe 8 Protro 'University Red' sports an engineered mesh upper with contrasting white pops, including an embroidered Swoosh and Kobe Bryant's signature sheath emblem on the tongue and heel. A full-length drop-in React foam midsole couples with a white rubber, herringbone traction pattern outsole and an exposed carbon fiber shank plate to keep feet stable on the court.

name: Jordan 4 Retro Hyper Violet (GS)
description: The Air Jordan 4 Retro GS 'Hyper Violet' brings a white leather upper with a padded mid-cut collar and breathable netting underneath. These shoes have bright violet eyelets, matching the molded support wings and the Jumpman logo adorning the tongue tag and back tab. The midsole includes an exposed Air-sole heel unit, anchored by a herringbone-patterned violet rubber outsole.

name: Converse CONS Chuck Taylor All Star Hi Pro Carhartt WIP Dark Earth
make: Converse CONS Chuck Taylor All Star Hi Pro
description: The Carhartt WIP x Converse Chuck Taylor All Star Pro High 'Starfish Dark Earth' brings a white suede upper on the inside of the foot and brown and tan panels on the outside. The Carhartt and Cons logos adorn the tongue, which includes lock-in elastic straps, and CX foam insoles. A sturdy brown rubber outsole keeps true to that skateboard-inspired look.

name: Nike Air Foamposite One Copper (2024)
description: Originally dropped in 2010 and retroed in 2017, this 2024 version of the Nike Air Foamposite One 'Copper' showcases a molded Foamposite upper in a coppery sheen. Contrasting black pops adorn the nubuck eyestay, knit collar and a Penny Hardaway-branded tongue. True to the original design, the see-through rubber outsole keeps the herringbone traction pods and a carbon fiber shank for midfoot stability.

name: Jordan 14 Retro Black Toe (2024) (GS)
description: The 2024 version of the Air Jordan 14 Retro GS 'Black Toe' sports a white leather upper with a black suede forefoot overlay, hence the name. A red Jumpman logo is embroidered on the toe box, joining a Jumpman emblem below the collar and an embossed one on the molded back tab. These shoes have a Phylon midsole equipped with springy Zoom Air cushioning. A herringbone-patterned rubber outsole works in tandem with a chrome-plated shank plate for midfoot stability.

name: Jordan 4 Retro Orchid (Women's)
description: The Women's Air Jordan 4 Retro 'Orchid' rolls out a lilac-colored suede upper with a visible side netting and grey molded eyelets. Speckled details adorn the support wings and molded back tab, adorned with the Jumpman logo, much like the foam midsole. Encapsulated Air-sole cushioning rests in the forefoot, while the heel equips an exposed Air bag for a soft feel underfoot.

name: Jordan 3 Retro Black Cat (2025)
description: The 2025 version of the Air Jordan 3 Retro 'Black Cat' was named after one of Michael Jordan's pre-NBA nicknames. Sporting black nubuck on the upper, these shoes have a matching black patent leather mudguard and charcoal elephant-print forefoot and heel overlays. The Jumpman logo graces the tongue and back tab, while a foam midsole contains a visible Air-sole heel unit for a resilient feel.

name: Jordan 3 Retro Black Cat (2025) (GS)
description: The 2025 iteration of the Air Jordan 3 Retro GS 'Black Cat' uses black nubuck on the upper, matching it with a patent leather mudguard and contrasting it with charcoal elephant-print overlays on the forefoot and heel areas. The Jumpman emblem decorates the tongue and molded heel tab to keep the iconic look. A matching black foam midsole gets a glossy finish, tooled with an Air-sole heel unit for a resilient feel.

name: Jordan 1 Retro High OG Black Toe Reimagined (GS)
description: The Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG GS 'Black Toe Reimagined' sports a crisp, white leather upper, adorned with black accents on the forefoot, collar and the iconic Swoosh. Red pops embellish the collar flap and heel overlay, the former stamped with an 'Air Jordan' wordmark instead of the traditional Wings logo. These grade school kicks have a traditional cupsole, adhered to an encapsulated Air-sole heel unit in the midsole.

name: Jordan 4 Retro Platinum Gold (GS)
description: Designed for grade schoolers, the Air Jordan 4 Retro GS 'Platinum Gold' dons a platinum leather upper with contrasting black netting on the side panel and throat. Black contrast on the forefoot overlay, molded eyelets, support wings and back tab provide a bold touch. The latter matches with a metallic gold Jumpman, while another reigns the tongue and sockliner. An off-white foam midsole contains an exposed Air-sole heel unit underfoot.

name: Jordan 1 Retro Low OG Howard University
description: The Air Jordan 1 Retro Low OG 'Howard University' dons the HBCU colors, using a white upper with navy touches on the Swoosh and forefoot overlay. A red heel and back tab match the mini Swoosh on the side of the forefoot, while the tongue rocks the customary Nike Air tag.

name: Jordan 11 Retro Bred Velvet (Women's)
description: The Women's Air Jordan 11 Retro 'Bred Velvet' shoes don a black velvet upper with a matching velvet mudguard in place of the traditional glossy patent leather overlay. Heritage details like the webbed eyelets and Jumpman logo below the collar remain intact. A white Phylon midsole pairs with a full-length Air-sole unit and anchored by a rubber outsole.

name: Jordan 11 Retro Legend Blue (2024) (GS)
description: The 2024 reissue of the Air Jordan 11 Retro GS 'Legend / Columbia' brings a white leather upper to go with a matching shiny patent leather mudguard. A light blue Jumpman logo adorns the collar, while a stylized '23' accents the black back tab. A lightweight Phylon midsole is equipped with a full-length Air-sole unit, and anchored by a blue rubber outsole.

name: Saucony ProGrid Omni 9 Starcow
description: The Starcow x Saucony ProGrid Omni 9 'Nature Acts, Man Does' lines the green mesh and suede upper in vibrant orange touches. Both logos adorn the tongue tag and insoles. More green pops land on the sculpted foam midsole, equipped with an exposed shank plate for midfoot containment.

name: Nike Kobe 6 Protro Sail All-Star
description: The Nike Zoom Kobe 6 Protro 'Sail', also known as 'All-Star 2.0', has an off-white knit upper covered in multiple stars on one side. The other side has a traditional scaly snakeskin pattern. A floating black Swoosh matches Kobe's shield logo on the tongue. A full-length Cushlon midsole contains a large and flexible Zoom Turbo unit in the forefoot.

name: Saucony ProGrid Triumph 4 Minted NY
description: The Minted New York x Saucony ProGrid Triumph 4 'Cream Green' combines white open-cell mesh with grey and silver synthetic overlays. Green trim outlines Saucony's river logo, matching the tongue tag stamped with Minted NY and Saucony logos. A lightweight foam midsole anchors the look alongside a decoupled rubber outsole.

name: UGG Classic Ultra Mini Boot Antilope (Women's)
description:
The UGG Classic Ultra Mini Antilope W are women-sized ankle boots that feature a suede upper and are available in an antelope brown color.

The Ultra Mini boots by UGG are designed with a brown suede upper crafted from sheepskin. The sheepskin suede upper is lightweight, and the thick and fluffy interior is made for warmth. Underfoot, the slip-in style classic ankle boots sit on a rubber outsole that rounds off the design.

The UGG Classic Ultra Mini Antilope W was originally released on the 1st of November 2021. The retail price was set at $140.

name: adidas Gazelle Bold Wonder White Clear Sky (Kids)
description: The adidas Gazelle Bold J 'Wonder White Clear Sky' rocks an off-white suede upper with white serrated leather three-stripes. A Powder blue leather back tab contrasts the design, while the Trefoil graces the tongue and a Gazelle signoff decorates the side printed in gold foil letters. A layered platform gum rubber midsole completes the vibe.

name: Jordan 1 Retro Low OG SP Travis Scott Velvet Brown
description: Travis Scott's signature reverse Swoosh stands out on the Air Jordan 1 Retro Low OG SP 'Velvet Brown', featuring a black tumbled leather upper with suede upper touches throughout. The brown nylon tongue gets a Nike Air tag, while mismatched Cactus Jack and Wings logos land on each back tab. A brown rubber cupsole gets stitched sidewalls and an encapsulated Air-sole heel unit for a plush sensation underfoot.

name: Nike Shox R4 Racer Blue Metallic Silver (Women's)
description: The Nike Women's Shox R4 'Blue Woman Group' dons a metallic silver Swoosh contrasting a blue leather upper. Mesh on the toe box keeps the feel airy, while a padded collar keeps you comfortable from the moment you lace them up. Instead of the traditional foam midsole, four compression foam columns lift the heel, providing a soft yet springy feel underfoot.

name: adidas GT II Sneakersnstuff London
description: The Sneakersnstuff x adidas GT 2 '1st Edition - London' is inspired from the '90s Stockholm rave scene, celebrating the Swedish retailer's 10th anniversary in the British capital. A green nylon upper with matching suede forefoot and heel overlays gets white leather accents on the three-stripes and back tab for contrast. Both logos adorn the tongue tag and insoles, while a gold foil 'SNS GTII' signoff embellishes the side. Thse shoes are anchored by a gum rubber sole unit.

Penny Hardaway's 1 Cent logo graces the tongue and back tab areas, while a see-through rubber outsole anchors the look.

name: Nike Zoom Vomero 5 Photon Dust Pink Foam (Women's)
description: The Nike Women's Air Zoom Vomero 5 'Photon Dust Pink Foam' uses multiple shades of pink on a full-length Cushlon foam midsole, which equips Zoom Air forefoot and heel units. The white, open-cell mesh upper gets a metallic silver Swoosh, 3M accents and mirror-reflective details on the eyestay and forefoot for an eye-catching look.

description: The G-Dragon x Nike Air Force 1 '07 'Para-Noise 3.0' rocks a black leather upper with mismatched Swoosh logos in hot pink, blue, yellow and teal. An embroidered daisy embellishes the tongue, while the Nike Air logo stars on the back tab. These shoes have a white rubber cupsole with prominent black scuff marks across the midsole.

name: Nike Dunk High Wu-Tang (2024)
description: The 2024 version of the Wu-Tang x Nike Dunk High Retro Premium spins it back to the 1999 design that was only available to friends and family. Based on the classic 'Iowa' Dunk' from Nike's original 'Be True to Your School' series, these shoes keep the black leather upper and complement it with Goldenrod overlays and a matching Swoosh. The Wu-Tang Clan's stylized 'W' logo adorns the tongue tag and side of the heel for a signature look.

name: Nike Air Max 1 Patta 20th Anniversary Chlorophyll
description: The 2024 edition of the Patta x Nike Air Max 1 'Chlorophyll' celebrates the Amsterdam-based label's 20th anniversary. Originally released in 2009, these shoes have a white mesh upper tooled with a grey leather midfoot overlay. Bright green knit pops on the mudguard and Swoosh enliven the look. A matching yet smaller Swoosh is embroidered on the forefoot, while the Patta emblem appears on the tongue tag and insoles.

name: Nike Dunk Low Retro University Blue
description: The Nike Dunk Low 'University Blue Coconut Milk' is decked out with an off-white leather upper, powder blue overlays and a matching Swoosh. A nylon tongue and perforated details on the toe box keep the OG details intact. A rubber cupsole gets white sidewalls and a blue rubber outsole for smooth traction.

name: Nike SB Dunk Low The Wizard of Oz Poppy Field
model: The Wizard of Oz Poppy Field
description: The Wizard of Oz x Nike Dunk Low SB 'Poppy Field' nods to the classic 1939 film. Red satin lines the upper, which is wrapped in a poppy field of Oz allover print. The silky top layer is made to be torn away, revealing a red suede surface, mirroring Dorothy's ruby slippers. The Nike SB and 'The Wizard of Oz' logos star on the tongue, while 'No place like home' is stitched on the heel. Nike SB-branded insoles depict the Wicked Witch of the West with one of her flying monkeys. The lively poppy print extends to the midsole, anchored by a red rubber outsole underfoot.

Pink synthetic leather overlays and a bright green mesh collar lining add a pop of color. A 'Savior' signoff lands on the heel, while the side showcases Jae Tip's flower logo. A beige foam midsole is anchored by a sturdy gum rubber outsole to finish the design.

description: Limited to only 500 pairs, the Alexis Sablone x Nike SB x Converse 'Chameleon Pack' dons a white tumbled leather upper with green, scaly-textured overlays, which have a wear-away top layer revealing a bright fuchsia color underneath. Moss green touches land on the scaly suede Swoosh and knit collar lining. The insoles have a Zoom Air heel unit for a soft feel underfoot. Consistent with the color-shifting 'Chameleon' theme, the Converse AS-1 Pro has a white pebbled leather upper that wears away, only to show hot pink underneath. CX foam insoles keep every step lightweight, while a herringbone-pattern gum rubber outsole keeps you surefooted.

name: UGG Lowmel Sand (Kids)
description:
The UGG Lowmel Sand (Kids) is a casual shoe with a soft, plush lining for added warmth and comfort. It has added padding for better foot and ankle support while your kid runs or plays. The shoe is a neutral shade of sand, making it versatile and suitable for wearing with an array of outfits. A sneaker design gives it a kid-friendly look and feel.

This shoe is part of the UGG's kid collection. UGG is a brand from Australia that is recognized for its shoes and boots, which are made of high-end materials like sheepskin. The UGG Lowmel Sand is made of suede and enhanced with recycled wool.

The UGG Lowmel Sand (Kids) features the label´s symbol embossed on the back of the shoe for brand identification. In addition to the overall design, our team likes the pattern of two-tone laces and heel strap, which makes the shoe easier to put on. UGG released this shoe on June 25th, 2024. It originally retailed for $100.

name: UGG Classic Ultra Mini Boot Chestnut
description:
The UGG Classic Ultra Mini Chestnut, which was made available for women, features overlock stitch detailing on its seams, and an asymmetrical topline.

The shoe is made of an upcycled wool upper made of Twinface sheepskin, a suede heel counter with a rear draw tab, a foam footbed, a lyocell insole, and a Treadlite outsole. The textile binding, which is created with polyester fibers recovered from other products, completes the look. An UGG-branded logo can be seen on the sewn heel. For traction, its outsole is chipped.

The UGG Classic Ultra Mini Chestnut debuted on November 1st, 2021, and originally retailed at $140.
